/02/21/minecraft-chemistry-update-goes-live.aspx |archive-date=26 February 2018 |access-date=8 March 2018 |publisher=The Journal}}</ref> free lesson plans available online, and two free companion applications: Code Connection and Classroom Mode.<ref>{{cite web |date=2 May 2017 |title=Minecraft: Education Edition: Five Fast Facts You Need to Know |url=https://heavy.com/games/2017/05/minecraft-education-edition-code-builder-learn-to-code-student-engagement-free-trial-price-subjects-age-range/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170502195005/https://heavy.com/games/2017/05/minecraft-education-edition-code-builder-learn-to-code-student-engagement-free-trial-price-subjects-age-range/ |archive-date=2 May 2017 |access-date=8 March 2018}}</ref>

