9 |access-date=5 October 2022}}</ref> YouTube later announced that on 14 December 2021 that the total amount of ''Minecraft''-related views on the website have exceeded one trillion.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/tech/gaming/minecraft-crosses-1-trillion-views-on-youtube-most-popular-game-ever-on-platform/ |title=Minecraft crosses 1 trillion views on YouTube, most popular game ever on platform |first=Ian |last=Sherr |date=14 December 2021 |access-date=14 December 2021 |work=[[CNet]]}}</ref>

